1. Naša reprezentacija je *zvanično* pobedila rivala. (Our national team has officially won the rival.) 
2. Svetsko prvenstvo je *zvanično* počelo. (The World Championship has officially begun.)
3. *Zvanično*, nema više anonimnih donacija. (Officially, there are no more anonymous donations.) 
4. Odluka je *zvanično* objavljena. (The decision was officially announced.)
5. *Zvanično*, nema nikakvih zakonskih prepreka. (Officially, there are no legal obstacles.)